{"word":"διψάω","slug":"διψάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διψάω</el></b> [<el>δίψα</el> ‘thirst’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δίψος\">δίψος</a></el>] <b><i>be thirsty</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in physical sense <b><a href='B:470 25:35'>Mt 25:35</a>; <a href='B:500 4:13'>J 4:13</a>; <a href='B:520 12:20'>Ro 12:20</a>; <a href='B:530 4:11'>1 Cor 4:11</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fig.\">fig.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of a, of longing for <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>: water of life <b><a href='B:500 4:14'>J 4:14</a>; <a href='B:500 6:35'>6:35</a>; <a href='B:500 7:37'>7:37</a>; <a href='B:730 21:6'>Rv 21:6</a>; <a href='B:730 22:17'>22:17</a>;</b> righteousness <b><a href='B:470 5:6'>Mt 5:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διχοτομέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δίψος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}